OL,3,CCould Channel Islands become a tax
OL,4,Chaven for 70,000 UK non-doms?
OL,6,FTax expert Thomas Adcock says: "It's
OL,7,Fnot that far away, the language is the
OL,8,Fsame of course, the legal system is
OL,9,Fsimilar and it's a beautiful place to
OL,10,Fbe."
OL,12,FBoth Jersey and Guernsey have tax
OL,13,Fregimes with no inheritance or capital
OL,14,Fgains that could benefit those
OL,15,Fconsidering their options.
