OL,3,CCould Channel Islands become a tax
OL,4,Chaven for 70,000 UK non-doms?
OL,6,FBut Dame Margaret Hodge MP from the
OL,7,FBritish Anti-Corruption and
OL,8,FResponsible Tax Group says the Channel
OL,9,FIslands should be more transparent in
OL,10,Ftheir financial affairs.
OL,12,FShe explained: "In the way that they
OL,13,Fchoose to administer their
OL,14,Fjurisdictions, they are causing a lot
OL,15,Fof damage not just to the UK but
OL,16,Facross the world."
