OL,3,CCould Channel Islands become a tax
OL,4,Chaven for 70,000 UK non-doms?
OL,6,FIn response to comments made by Ms
OL,7,FHodge, the Government of Jersey
OL,8,Fdescribes itself as having "one of the
OL,9,Fmost established beneficial ownership
OL,10,Fregisters in the world".
OL,12,FIt says: "The register was first
OL,13,Festablished in 1989 and contains
OL,14,Finformation which is reliable,
OL,15,Faccurate, verified and that is already
OL,16,Freadily available to international law
OL,17,Fenforcement and tax authorities.
