OL,6,F"Independent international evaluations
OL,7,Fhave confirmed Jersey has a 'leading
OL,8,Fposition' concerning beneficial
OL,9,Fownership transparency.
OL,11,F"Despite this position, it is
OL,12,Fregrettable and misleading that
OL,13,Finaccurate descriptions of the
OL,14,Fposition in Jersey persist."
OL,16,FThis is ultimately a debate about
OL,17,Fwhether the islands want to be the
OL,18,Fplace people turn to when they want to
OL,19,Fpay less tax.
